# Etch — AI agent session capture (local WIP buffers; records live in git refs).
# On this PUBLIC repo capture is LOCAL-ONLY: no refspec, and settings.json
# (hostname salt) stays untracked. The carve-out keeps the block identical to
# the private-repo standard.
.etch/*
!.etch/settings.json

